\newlabel{fig:ifopng_comparison}{{5}{27}{\textbf {iFOPNG vs.\ FOPNG across six benchmarks (Sub-RQ3).} Grouped bars show mean average accuracy; circles show individual seeds; error bars show $\pm 1$ standard deviation. The dashed vertical line separates standalone (left) from hypernetwork (right) settings. \texttt {iFOPNG} uses the combined metric $F_c = \hat {F}_\mathrm {new} + \hat {F}_\mathrm {old}$; \texttt {FOPNG} uses only $\hat {F}_\mathrm {new}$}{figure.caption.36}{}}
